description: Golden Chipmunk is a PFP project published by Singular, which combines the Singular Genesis token function. The image of Golden Chipmunk comes from the shrewd and capable chipmunks, also known as golden chipmunks. Golden chipmunks are smart and clever, good at searching and storing their 'wealth' - those rich nuts, just like all you and me who walk through the Web3 world, we are good at discovering the wealth of the blockchain world.
name: Golden Chipmunk
